{"tid":334734,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港府消息：出租非割地但非施香港法律　廁所都由中國管","createTime":"2017-07-25T04:01:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-26T16:25:03.000Z","uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e16b23e8d05a14dcb9b9ca8f56935abfb6db48c2","tid":334734,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T04:01:31.000Z","msg":"政府研究近7年的高鐵一地兩檢方案，預料今早會在行政會議討論，最快下午對外公開。政府消息指，高鐵西九站最低兩層會參考深圳灣租貸形式予內地當局，特區政府仍擁有業權，強調在一國下並不存在割讓土地，因香港屬中國。<br />\n<br />\n至於外界關注內地執法權限，消息指，基本上所有人進在香港入境櫃位辦理離境手續，進入內地樓層時已進入內地邊境，就需遵守內地法律，「即係嗰兩層連電梯、廁所等範圍都屬於內地規管」。<br />\n<br />\n消息指，若在內地規管範圍涉及刑事罪行，不排除相關涉案人士被送往內地調查，「如果喺嗰度示威，好似早前有人喺羅湖橋度宣讀《零八憲章》，內地深圳邊境當局都只係問話完遣送返嚟香港，內地從來無刑事檢控過香港示威者」。但消息承認部分駐守西九站的內地執法者會"},{"pid":"73684f64a7a0c057b482fe6640e088c35673198b","tid":334734,"uid":1441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T04:04:27.000Z","msg":"出租<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />即係違反基本法啦"},{"pid":"32320ea57fe634e14f2fd342ba4ce8230f1baab2","tid":334734,"uid":54373,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T04:06:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://sa1.bbkz.net/forum/attachment.php?s=f5ea1e6c91a0dbd34d61f01cfbc0691d&amp;attachmentid=884807&amp;thumb=1&amp;d=1370701703\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsa1.bbkz.net%2Fforum%2Fattachment.php%3Fs%3Df5ea1e6c91a0dbd34d61f01cfbc0691d%26attachmentid%3D884807%26thumb%3D1%26d%3D1370701703&h=4c2b1fb2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6b5060e38b69e9c2818e38fac08f36822c4b4ba9","tid":334734,"uid":1082,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T04:09:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>出租<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />即係違反基本法啦</blockquote><br />\n其實如果中國同香港真係一國，應該連租都唔洗。<br />\n從來都係無物件主權既人向有物份主權既人租野用，從來未聽過業主向租客租返佢自己個單位既一間房<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51c66829d650500830dd2f2059d968f80e1961cc","tid":334734,"uid":26385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T04:11:38.000Z","msg":"法租界英租界你又講到係民族恥辱咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n出租非割地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4116461b33b2acd0c8fe2f9e293f46533654ae73","tid":334734,"uid":1082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T04:16:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>法租界英租界你又講到係民族恥辱咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n出租非割地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n當時政府無話係恥辱，係後人話係姐<br />\n實在清朝都有租人啲地<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/仁川清租界\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hk%2F%E4%BB%81%E5%B7%9D%E6%B8%85%E7%A7%9F%E7%95%8C&d=CtS3Nn%2BaoEd%2BECsNizbbEtibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=e939fdeb\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/仁川清租界</a>"},{"pid":"0113accacf9972a1cdf21f4035c3ea0317cb5635","tid":334734,"uid":33797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T04:16:50.000Z","msg":"共狗可唔可以租全港一年玩下先<br />\n<br />\n租咗唔還<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4310f5f2060fc95ea058da76043c55f634f4db6","tid":334734,"uid":1082,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T04:28:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>出租<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />即係違反基本法啦</blockquote><br />\n其實如果中國同香港真係一國，應該連租都唔洗。<br />\n從來都係無物件主權既人向有物份主權既人租野用，從來未聽過業主向租客租返佢自己個單位既一間房<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n由呢一點可以睇得出， 中國實際上無香港主權， 中國同香港關係實際上應該係香港係中國既附庸國或者保護國。 之所以用一國兩制做包裝，只不過想隱瞞呢個事實，同埋想加快吞並進程（1997年一take 搞掂)，同時又唔受國際壓力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2bafb4eaa2c61fb8dfaa0a62f99c17139ab4de3","tid":334734,"uid":17866,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T05:33:00.000Z","msg":"出租先例一開，日後會慢慢「租」曬全香港<br />\n<br />\nSimple like shit"},{"pid":"a6c29a2118ccf9736068e85b0c0ad2bdcb4b4208","tid":334734,"uid":34872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T05:42:44.000Z","msg":"同當年英國殖民地一樣 簽租約"},{"pid":"6f1d8fbc1f8860d5e84d0bc40b15b86b6c2e8d61","tid":334734,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T06:47:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2dcb8b75b5c48aa603363c7b64b42d79b185c771","tid":334734,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T06:48:43.000Z","msg":"回歸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咪又係殖民地"},{"pid":"70e039985a933e3fdcdcb3a007c0b15821e03bd5","tid":334734,"uid":53687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T06:52:02.000Z","msg":"畀幾多錢租先？<br />\n租金幾多落市民袋？"},{"pid":"daf26126dc7683355186f724ab49bf89b9d41307","tid":334734,"uid":55924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T08:05:35.000Z","msg":"出租予外國人士可突破蘿本法限制😱"},{"pid":"33206fef3ec42d3a1d5963d325e315dd1860cafa","tid":334734,"uid":67292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T08:10:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>出租<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />即係違反基本法啦</blockquote><br />\n其實如果中國同香港真係一國，應該連租都唔洗。<br />\n從來都係無物件主權既人向有物份主權既人租野用，從來未聽過業主向租客租返佢自己個單位既一間房<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n傻啦，如果你業主真係租左出去，可以話收返就收返既咩? 簽晒合同話唔可以收返，唔可以佔用，你估業主就大晒?"},{"pid":"b1fc823126a9a39c32d6daf105a50a23ea2c9874","tid":334734,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T08:21:35.000Z","msg":"千幾億成本，連同每年營運開支，你收得幾多錢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n賤賣資產"},{"pid":"2fa0a09043fd888fc246c7baba4deb01d91c66cb","tid":334734,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T09:07:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00e53bc511e7870c18dc247c898ff79175e486ef","tid":334734,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T10:27:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d24de5416f4d4fd12f2ee69cb75460de9e1acb8","tid":334734,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T11:45:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"318a43177bb94198d5a16b688342c60dbcfb9d85","tid":334734,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T11:53:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f739b41073af459e4db3b78c61000f5ec5a493fe","tid":334734,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T12:20:38.000Z","msg":"廁所搵中國大媽負責<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n臭到"},{"pid":"6c67c69d3d31728c3757b19a68f574dacd3dc522","tid":334734,"uid":1082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T15:37:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>出租<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />即係違反基本法啦</blockquote><br />\n其實如果中國同香港真係一國，應該連租都唔洗。<br />\n從來都係無物件主權既人向有物份主權既人租野用，從來未聽過業主向租客租返佢自己個單位既一間房<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n傻啦，如果你業主真係租左出去，可以話收返就收返既咩? 簽晒合同話唔可以收返，唔可以佔用，你估業主就大晒?</blockquote><br />\n屌， 比強國遠抄左個例子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3989ec2c5dd258b7c77e6da86a2abb87c357d3f","tid":334734,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T16:25:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}